cycle costs. Projects are development efforts to upgrade systems that have been fielded or have received approval for full rate production and anticipate production
funding in the current or subsequent fiscal year.

 Project 1427, Surface Tactical Team Trainer (STTT) develops upgrades during the sustainment phase of the Battle Force Tactical Training (BFTT) system and its
