E. Acquisition Strategy
GMTI is a Major Defense Acquisition Program, Acquisition Category 1B. In August 2024, the USSF Service Acquisition Executive approved the program at Milestone B
to enter the Engineering Manufacturing and Development Phase and proceed to the Deployment and Operations and Support phases. The Space Force will present the
GMTI system and forces to the Combatant Commands under Title 10 authority to enable kill chain closure and battle management functions. Additional details can be
provided under separate cover.

 The FY 2024 budget for GMTI was transferred from USAF to Department of the Air Force in the FY 2024 DAA.
 The FY 2025 budget for GMTI was transferred from USAF to USSF in the Full-Year Continuing Appropriations and Extensions Act, 2025.




