digital engineering, provide oversight of Title X systems engineering functions, and implement software, data, cyber, and
engineering frameworks, guidance, and governance to improve product delivery and cyber operational readiness for fielded
systems. Additionally, this project has influence over program budgets for acquisition programs of record. General Officer
(GO) / SES collaboration is required with key stakeholders across the Army, OSD, and other services, including the U.S. Army
Training and Doctrine Command (TRADOC); U.S. Army Futures Command (AFC); Chief Information Officer (CIO); U.S. Army
