The ARC-190 legacy radio is End of Life (EOL) and no longer procurable. The scope of the work includes, but is not limited to, the replacement of the existing ARC-190
system with an ARC-260 Remote Control Unit (RCU) and Receiver/Transmitter (R/T). The current program intent is to reuse the existing HF antenna/coupler and reuse
