Title: Stage 1 Battery Replacement (SOBR)                                                                                                         3.060       8.556        15.275
Description: The current Stage 1 (SE-13G) battery has exceeded its projected shelf life and recent aging surveillance testing
shows adverse impacts to reliability and availability. As a result, the batteries are not expected to last for the extended MM III
lifespan. This program will replace the aging silver zinc Stage 1 battery utilizing newer technologies to develop and produce a
thermal battery to extend the MM III lifespan through the transition period to Sentinel.

